<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 18:16:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国财政部扩大对军事基地附近土地交易的安全审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-treasury-expand-security-reviews-land-deals-near-military-bases-2024-07-08/</link><description>美国财政部周一宣布大幅扩大对外国购买美国军事基地附近房地产的安全审查权限，将 30 个州的 56 个设施列入其审查名单。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 17:06:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-treasury-expand-security-reviews-land-deals-near-military-bases-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>商务部表示，中国对中欧电动汽车关税谈判表现出“最大诚意”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-has-shown-utmost-sincerity-over-china-eu-ev-tariff-talks-ministry-says-2024-07-08/</link><description>中国商务部周一表示，中国对欧盟电动汽车补贴调查相关磋商表现出“最大诚意”，欧盟官员的言论“与事实严重不符”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 15:12:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-has-shown-utmost-sincerity-over-china-eu-ev-tariff-talks-ministry-says-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>胜利者斯维托丽娜在温网为乌克兰佩戴黑丝带</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/svitolina-wears-black-ribbon-ukraine-reaches-wimbledon-quarters-2024-07-08/</link><description>埃琳娜·斯维托丽娜周一闯入温布尔登四分之一决赛，但对于这位泪流满面的乌克兰人来说，结果是次要的。在俄罗斯空袭基辅一家儿童医院后，她的思绪与祖国同在。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 14:56:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/svitolina-wears-black-ribbon-ukraine-reaches-wimbledon-quarters-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>德国经济部长表示关税竞赛是“错误的”并将推高物价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tariff-race-is-wrong-will-push-up-prices-says-german-economy-minister-2024-07-08/</link><description>德国经济部长罗伯特·哈贝克 (Robert Habeck) 批评关税损害了经济和消费者，几天前，欧盟委员会不顾欧洲汽车行业的强烈抗议，提议对中国制造的电动汽车征收高达 37.9% 的关税。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 13:05:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tariff-race-is-wrong-will-push-up-prices-says-german-economy-minister-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国比亚迪计划投资 8.94 亿美元的电动汽车零部件项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-plans-894-mln-ev-parts-project-state-media-says-2024-07-08/</link><description>据《证券时报》周一报道，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪已签署协议，建设一家新能源汽车核心零部件工厂，总投资达 65 亿元人民币（合 8.942 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 12:21:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-plans-894-mln-ev-parts-project-state-media-says-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，宝马寻求降低中国制造的电动Mini的进口关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-seeks-lower-import-tariffs-china-made-electric-mini-source-says-2024-07-08/</link><description>据一位知情人士透露，宝马已要求布鲁塞尔计算其中国制造的电动 Mini 向欧洲的进口关税，目前根据欧盟临时法规，该车须缴纳最高关税。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 11:31:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-seeks-lower-import-tariffs-china-made-electric-mini-source-says-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国山东省计划到2025年锂电池产业规模达140亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-shandong-province-plans-14-bln-lithium-battery-industry-by-2025-2024-07-08/</link><description>周一当地政府的一份通知显示，中国山东省计划到明年发展价值 1000 亿元人民币（138 亿美元）的锂电池产业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 11:14:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-shandong-province-plans-14-bln-lithium-battery-industry-by-2025-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体猛烈抨击中储粮涉嫌使用油轮运输食用油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-state-media-slams-sinograin-over-alleged-use-fuel-tankers-transport-2024-07-08/</link><description>中国官方媒体周一批评国家粮食储备公司中储粮，此前当地媒体报道称，该公司的油轮也被用来运输食用油，引发食品安全担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:56:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-state-media-slams-sinograin-over-alleged-use-fuel-tankers-transport-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：股市创新高，法国出人意料</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>德国商报报道，ASML 首席执行官表示世界需要中国生产的传统芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-world-needs-legacy-chips-china-is-producing-handelsblatt-reports-2024-07-08/</link><description>设备制造商ASML首席执行官在周一发表的德国商报采访中表示，包括德国汽车行业在内的芯片买家需要中国芯片制造商目前正在投资的老一代计算机芯片。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-world-needs-legacy-chips-china-is-producing-handelsblatt-reports-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯官员称美国离开武器条约是为了制造武器威胁中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-official-says-us-left-arms-treaty-build-weapons-menace-china-2024-07-08/</link><description>俄罗斯副外长谢尔盖·里亚布科夫周一指责美国决定退出苏联时代的军控条约，以便华盛顿可以开始制造武器来恐吓中国。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-official-says-us-left-arms-treaty-build-weapons-menace-china-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>摩根大通下调新兴市场企业违约预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-cuts-forecast-emerging-market-corporate-defaults-2024-07-08/</link><description>投资银行摩根大通周一下调了对预计出现债务违约的新兴市场公司数量的预测，此前陷入困境的市场定价出现了自 2016 年以来的最大改善。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:01:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-cuts-forecast-emerging-market-corporate-defaults-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾军舰“损坏”南海环礁岛礁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-claims-philippine-warships-damaged-reef-atoll-south-china-sea-2024-07-08/</link><description>中国周一表示，菲律宾军舰在南海南沙群岛“非法”搁浅，“严重破坏”了该地区的珊瑚礁生态系统，两国在这片广阔水道上的环礁上存在争议领土。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-claims-philippine-warships-damaged-reef-atoll-south-china-sea-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度将于7月试行从蒙古进口炼焦煤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-get-coking-coal-mongolia-trial-basis-july-sources-say-2024-07-08/</link><description>两位知情人士称，印度将从本月晚些时候开始试行从蒙古进口炼焦煤，新德里寻求实现关键炼钢原材料进口多元化，以减少对澳大利亚的过度依赖。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:46:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-get-coking-coal-mongolia-trial-basis-july-sources-say-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利政府寻求更多企业捐款，限制媒体资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/hungary-seeking-defence-contribution-multinational-firms-banks-energy-sector-2024-07-08/</link><description>匈牙利政府周一制定了所谓的“反战”行动计划，寻求银行、能源和跨国公司的捐款，并针对其指责支持乌克兰战争的媒体的外国资助。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/hungary-seeking-defence-contribution-multinational-firms-banks-energy-sector-2024-07-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>